dataStudio.name: Health Imaging Connector
dataStudio.description: Health data from Vendor Neutral Archives. Including MRI/CT and X-Ray imaging. (https://omniindex/io/datastudio). This connector allows you to create dashboards within Google Data Studio from you imaging devices. To use this Connector, your organization must have an available OmniIndex Health Platform instance. Please contact our support team, if you have any questions.
dataStudio.shortDescription: Health data from Vendor Neutral Archives. Including MRI/CT and X-Ray imaging
